a.n: Launch Party: James Bond No Time To Die

p.k: It's a first for Launch Party, as we celebrate the release of the 25th instalment of the Bond movie franchise, No Time To Die. From Oddjob to Alec Trevelyan, Goldfinger to Jaws... the 007 films and games have certainly left their mark on moviegoers and gamers alike. Get your trigger finger ready for some Bond. James Bond.
